            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1592297249779-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add the <strong>lamb mince</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>half</strong> the <strong>sumac</strong> (save the rest for later), <strong>ground cumin </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the spices are fully mixed in</p><p>Divide the <strong>lamb</strong> <strong>mixture</strong> into 10 <span class=\"text-danger\">[20]</span>, shape them into meatballs and flatten them slightly</p><p>Tip: Use wet hands to shape the balls!</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
