          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a dry, large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> lamb kofte</strong> and cook for 4-5 min on each side or until golden and cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
